 391    roundPower2MonoLevel(ca,dt)             'HVDC sent value above which one pole is stopped and therefore FIR cannot use round power'
 392    bipole2MonoLevel(ca,dt)                 'HVDC sent value below which one pole is available to start in the opposite direction and therefore SIR can use round power'
