 445    InitialLoad(ca,dt,n)                                'Value that represents the Pnode load MW at the start of the solution interval. Depending on the inputs this value will be either actual load, an operator applied override or an estimated initial load'
 446    LoadIsScalable(ca,dt,n)                             'Binary value. If True then the Pnode InitialLoad will be scaled in order to calculate nodedemand, if False then Pnode InitialLoad will be directly assigned to nodedemand'
