 462  Scalars
 463  * Violation penalties
 464  * These violation penalties are not specified in the model formulation document (ver.4.3) but are specified in the
 465  * document "Resolving Infeasibilities & High Spring Washer Price situations - an overview" available at www.systemoperator.co.nz/n2766,264.html
 466    deficitBusGenerationPenalty                      'Bus deficit violation penalty'                      /500000/
 467    surplusBusGenerationPenalty                      'Bus surplus violation penalty'                      /500000/
 468    deficitBrCstrPenalty                             'Deficit branch group constraint violation penalty'  /650000/
 469    surplusBrCstrPenalty                             'Surplus branch group constraint violation penalty'  /650000/
 470    deficitGnrcCstrPenalty                           'Deficit generic constraint violation penalty'       /710000/
 471    surplusGnrcCstrPenalty                           'Surplus generic constraint violation penalty'       /710000/
 472    deficitRampRatePenalty                           'Deficit ramp rate violation penalty'                /850000/
 473    surplusRampRatePenalty                           'Surplus ramp rate violation penalty'                /850000/
 474    deficitBranchFlowPenalty                         'Deficit branch flow violation penalty'              /600000/
 475    surplusBranchFlowPenalty                         'Surplus branch flow violation penalty'              /600000/
 476    deficitMnodeCstrPenalty                          'Deficit market node constraint violation penalty'   /700000/
 477    surplusMnodeCstrPenalty                          'Surplus market node constraint violation penalty'   /700000/
 478    DeficitReservePenalty_CE                         '6s and 60s CE reserve deficit violation penalty'    /100000/
 479    DeficitReservePenalty_ECE                        '6s and 60s ECE reserve deficit violation penalty'   /800000/
